---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Library" description="Books I've read on programming and history.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Library</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>Programming</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Test-Driven Development with Python (2nd Edition)</li>
      <li>Two Scoops of Django 1.11: Best Practices for the Django Web Framework</li>
      <li>Web Scraping with Python: Collecting Data from the Modern Web</li>
      <li>Flask Web Development: Developing Web Applications with Python (2nd Edition)</li>
      <li>Fluent Python: Clear, Concise, and Effective Programming</li>
      <li>Python Cookbook (3rd Edition)</li>
      <li>Python Pocket Reference: Python In Your Pocket (5th Edition)</li>
      <li>Pro AngularJS</li>
      <li>AngularJS: Up and Running</li>
      <li>JavaScript: The Good Parts</li>
      <li>JavaScript Patterns: Build Better Applications with Coding and Design Patterns</li>
      <li>Modern PHP: New Features and Good Practices</li>
      <li>PHP Cookbook: Solutions &amp; Examples for PHP Programmers (3rd Edition)</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="project-category">
    <h2>History</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Thirty Years That Shook Physics</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
